75.2.4 Procuring Entities shall adopt Fit-for-Purpose and Proportional procurement approaches to encourage the participation of registered bidders from vulnerable and marginalized sectors, microenterprises, social enterprises, and startups. The measures to be adopted include, but are not limited to:

